# Project conventions

- Training logic lives in `src/modeling/`; entry points are `src/train.py` and `src/eval.py`.
- Hydra configs under `configs/`; run outputs go to `outputs/` (gitignored).
- Research state under `research/`.
- Do not commit `.env`, API keys, or `outputs/`.
- In `hitl` mode (see `research/research_state.yaml`), do not advance pipeline phases without human approval.
